TitMainTitle: Crowd of women and men, including one on right wearing dark cap, eyeglasses, light colored shirt, light colored sweater, dark jacket, and dark pants, standing with hands in pockets, gathered on sidewalk in front of brick building with storefront and signs in windows that read "This Store Will Close at 6:00 PM Wednesday December 31st" and "Thursday January 1 This Store Will Be Closed New Years Day" with keystone, possibly a state liquor store
